entry.title: 48" Single Sink Vanity Set with Mirror (Shaker White)
entry.summary:
Vendor: Builderz Warehouse
Type: Bathroom Vanities 26" to 48"
Price: 1345.00

A perfect complement to a contemporary space, the Builderz Warehouse bathroom vanity combines the clean, sharp lines of modern design with classic furniture styling. The carrara white marble countertop provides a dramatic contrast with the white/grey cabinet. Simple, bar-style pulls and knobs adorn the spacious drawers and doors, which conceal ample storage space for all your bathroom accoutrements.

Bathroom Vanity Size:
48″W × 22″D × 34”H
Bathroom Vanity Finishing:
Matt White/Grey
Cabinet Material:
Solid wood(Birch/rubber wood) + plywood ( CARB certification)
Cabinet Construction:
Undermount wash basin
Soft-closing doors
Soft-closing drawers
Cabinet Hardwares:
DTC/BLUM soft-close hinges and brushed nickel handles
Counter-top Optional:
White Carrara marble
Wash Basin:
18-20inch under-mounted Rectangle, CUPC certificated

entry.title: 30" Floating Single Sink Vanity Set -Gray
entry.summary:
Vendor: Wayfair
Type: Bathroom Vanities 26" to 48"
Price: 525.00

This is a 30" traditional floating vanity with raised sink. It's stylish and priced to fit any budget. This Genoa vanity is crafted from gray plywood carcass and features a 4" thick double layer white quartz top with vessel rectangle sink. (Faucet sold separately). This product is not available for shipping and must be picked up at our Phoenix location.

 
• Measures 30" W X 20 7/8" D X 18" H.
• Fully-extending undermount soft close drawer slides with drawers in natural wood.
• Dovetail drawer joints.
• Aluminum pulls.
